    <owl:Ontology rdf:about="https://purl.org/eudpp/IDENT">
        <dcterms:contributor xml:lang="en">Riina Maigre</dcterms:contributor>
        <dcterms:created xml:lang="en">2026-04-13</dcterms:created>
        <dcterms:creator xml:lang="en">Tarmo Robal</dcterms:creator>
        <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">MODULE: IDENT
Identifier module of the EU DPP core ontology proposal of the CIRPASS-2 European project.

The Identifier module proposes an universal approach for identifiers used in the EU DPP CO delivered by the CIRPASS-2 European Project.  
The module describes identifiers used for the project through aspects and scheme references, if appropriate, granularity is added.
---

DESIGN RESTRICTION: Specific modules of the EU DPP CO need to use the Connector to establish a link to the Identifiers module. The link needs to be establsihed to a subclass of aIdentifier class, e.g., Product hasUniqueProductIdentifier ProductIdentifier.
---

DEPENDENCIES: This module may have dependencies to all  EU DPP Core Ontology (CO) modules that use different types of identifiers, including: CON, P_DPP, SOC, ACTOR, ...  
--

THIS DOCUMENT IS PROVIDED WITH NO WARRANTIES WHATSOEVER. 
All liability for any damages arising from use or misuse of this vocabulary is with the user.</dcterms:description>
        <dcterms:issued xml:lang="en">2026-04-28</dcterms:issued>
        <dcterms:licence rdf:resource="https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0"/>
